root: ^Hey, whale! Thought I'd swing by and see how you're doing.
^Oh! Look who's back. Thanks for dropping by, friend.
^No worries. How's the ocean treating you?
^I've been exploring all sorts of new spots.
^And those fruits you brought me really hit the spot!
^Glad to hear it! Did you find anything exciting?
^If you haven't already, you should swim across to the other side of our island!
^I will do that! Thanks for the tip, catch you later!
^Take care, fox friend. See you around!
